{"tid":1777379,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟通過magnitsky act無人講","createTime":"2019-12-10T07:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T08:47:19.000Z","uid":82482,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"daf68f8755a1eae305a6c24d45485a4c16d6639c","tid":1777379,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc17be27cae8da602968c939c72cca2d0b19f1aa","tid":1777379,"uid":321374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:43:54.000Z","msg":"唔係通過左開file ja 咩？"},{"pid":"9f2c5db3794ec36c8b7164f18d49ca999d4b7423","tid":1777379,"uid":249263,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:50:23.000Z","msg":"正視聽 唔係通過哂<br />\n係開始啟動立法程序<br />\n但都需要我地去提出中共侵害人權的證據<br />\n<br />\n（Twitter戰線）歐盟Magnitsky Act有重要進程<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">twitter要人: 歐盟今日啟動Magnitsky Act 立法程序，詳細議會仲要傾，但歐洲戰線開啟左啦，快啲入去講邊個國家的人最需要被裁裁啦！！</span><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n幫手入去retweet同推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"223522d589cae33fc0850f3e36e2fa00f62ec8c4","tid":1777379,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:29:44.000Z","msg":"fc 未"},{"pid":"5d16e5ce5a97773a8ca21a378396917f2cabe56e","tid":1777379,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:39:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「立法工作啟動」</span></span>咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2019/12/blog-post_10.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feuropechinese.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F12%2Fblog-post_10.html&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cWLrBTEyyW%2B%2F%2BTJtsqEcrWg%3D&h=7a17c2b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2019/12/blog-post_10.html</a><br />\n<br />\n// 今天（10日）是全球人權日之際，歐盟昨天（9日）就全球人權議題作出重大決定，由新任歐盟外交高級代表博雷（Josep Borrell，照片來自歐盟網站）首次主持的歐盟外長會議作出一系列決定，當中包括「就可能的制裁機制以處理嚴重人權侵犯，啟動準備工作」。簡單來說，就是「歐盟版《馬格尼茨基法》」（The Magnitsky Act）的<span style=\"color: gold;\">法案草擬工作正式啟動。</span>//<br />\n<br />\n// 事實上，除了經貿及科技產業以外，歐盟現時很多潛在對付中國（或是香港人希望歐盟用來對付中國）的措施，很多其實原本都是<span style=\"color: gold;\">用來對付俄羅斯</span>，但一旦需要的話，用來對付中國是更方便。<br />\n<br />\n以針對官媒為例，歐美一直批評俄羅斯國營媒體RT在西方散播假新聞，研究是否立例限制他們在本國的活動，但至今都做不到，因為你就算幾不滿RT也好，他們確實經營得好像BBC、DW、澳洲ABC等西方的公共廣播機構，你很難完全指摘RT，倒是新華社、央視、《人民日報》，不單是架構上屬政府組織，在習近平年代，中國政府講明媒體「姓黨」，西方要寫一條法例禁絕這些中國官媒，十分容易。一些人在討論對付俄國RT時便指出，如果真的立了相關法例，第一個被趕出西方的是新華社，而非RT。//"},{"pid":"b0abd7684a48078bddb85d3cfa2873d6dd31b61a","tid":1777379,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:47:19.000Z","msg":"戇鳩樓豬"}]}